************************************************

Arduino CC1101 driver, SWAP stack, application library and sample code
for the panStamp. PanStamp is a low-power wireless board programmable
from the Arduino IDE.

Web sites:
http://www.panstamp.com
http://panstamp.blogspot.com 

************************************************

================================================
	v0.0.4 (Jul/04/2011)
================================================
- New disableAddressCheck method in CC1101 class
- Corrections on some EEPROM procedures

================================================
	v0.0.3 (Apr/26/2011)
================================================
- "Endpoint" renamed as "register" in the scope of the SWAP protocol
- A single register can now contain multiple endpoints

================================================
	v0.0.2 (Mar/21/2011)
================================================
- Corrections on the transmission of the security nonce

================================================
	v0.0.1 (Mar/18/2011)
================================================
- First version

